section.section:
Of the seven Board members:
One shall be from the Department of the Environment;
One shall be from the Department of Natural Resources;
One shall be a public member; and
Four shall be licensed master well drillers who are actively practicing well drilling at the time of appointment and shall include:
One from Caroline, Cecil, Dorchester, Kent, Queen Anne's, Somerset, Talbot, Wicomico, or Worcester county;
One from Baltimore City or Baltimore, Carroll, Harford, Howard, or Montgomery county;
One from Anne Arundel, Calvert, Charles, Prince George's, or St. Mary's county; and
One from Allegany, Frederick, Garrett, or Washington county.
